{"tid":211354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本治安亮紅燈？ 銀座商人當街遭搶4千萬日圓","createTime":"2017-04-21T14:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T04:03:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c24f48caf3f3870f93dd93ac68c5c7501569b0bc","tid":211354,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpNTE4I5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpNTE4I5.jpg&h=be19098f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本東京銀座鬧區，一名40歲商人在光天化日下被男子搶走手上千萬現金。（法新社）</span><br />\n2017-04-21  21:18<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本九州福岡市昨（20）日才剛發生一起3.8億日圓（約新台幣1億800萬）的駭人搶案，今日下午在東京最熱鬧的銀座地區，竟也當街發生搶案，一名男子當時手提高達千萬日圓的手提袋，就在眾目睽睽之下被劫走，連2天巨額搶案引發日本民眾譁然。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/apr/21/images/bigPic/400_400/phpF2GyNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fapr%2F21%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpF2GyNA.jpg&h=642145f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京警視廳在案發當場拉起封鎖線，積極尋找犯案者線索。（法新社）<br />\n綜合日媒報導，當地時間下午1點20分左右，在東京銀座5丁目街頭，一名40歲的男性商人剛結束業務接洽，手裡提著7200萬日圓（約新台幣2000多萬）的鉅款，走在路上時卻突然遭一名男子從背後襲擊並猛踢他的腹部，隨後奪取他的手提袋，強盜倉皇逃離時，將部分現金灑落在地，但仍有約4000萬現金（約新台幣1113萬）被劫走。<br />\n現場目擊者指出，犯案男子當時穿著藍色運動服及牛仔褲，而據警方調閱的監視錄影器顯示，除了主要犯案者之外，當時疑有另1名同夥騎乘黑色機車接應，並朝新橋車站方向逃離現場，警方懷疑這起案件為集體犯案。<br />\n連續2天的街頭搶案讓日本當地人心惶惶，東京警視廳目前正在緊急查緝該男子身分。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2043874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2043874&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTif%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5a2edc4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2043874&h=ee3def2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2043874</a>"},{"pid":"f11cfabe8794c088472ed96b03eb245331273349","tid":211354,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb67280180ccf1a5efc6737c29e1f4fac4e8cf8","tid":211354,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"日本啲賊都好過其他國家 無搶哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留返少少比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2ed90a835efe5075d4a5c99202937c3ef91b39","tid":211354,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:59:33.000Z","msg":"咁多CAM都敢搶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9564b4995b905f099762f13c08c92f7f72cb1a67","tid":211354,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"好搶唔搶咁啱<br />\n應該有內鬼"},{"pid":"2f5ccc5432d32842e29fdb45b0bb0c30c5efad7a","tid":211354,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好搶唔搶咁啱<br />\n應該有內鬼</blockquote><br />\n咪就係 可能呃保險添"},{"pid":"24e49dc6d5f775457e39b701e086bc2577140963","tid":211354,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:27:07.000Z","msg":"太多中國遊客"},{"pid":"ca361a4a90d132042c6b1afc63a9974de6d94a4b","tid":211354,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:32:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74d7b94e6fd71e22a295c3230499ea33b301531d","tid":211354,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:35:57.000Z","msg":"似有鬼多"},{"pid":"3b88a3843d61b2620abb855da42c6fe670e28dde","tid":211354,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6431348b91e88b5f6656e6473d5b4656f08effcd","tid":21